---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Workspace Architecture">
  <div class="markdown-content">
    <p>This project leverages a multi-crate Cargo workspace to separate core API logic from interface boundaries and client integrations.</p>

    <h2>Directory Layout</h2>
    <pre><code>dnz/
├── Cargo.toml                 # Root workspace manifest
├── pixi.toml                  # Local environment config
├── docs/                      # Astro documentation (this portal)
├── .github/                   # CI/CD verification workflows
└── crates/
    ├── dnz-core/              # Library containing core API wrappers
    │   ├── src/
    │   │   ├── client.rs      # HTTP client and backoff retry structures
    │   │   ├── models.rs      # Serde schemas mapping DigitalNZ API JSON
    │   │   ├── dataframe.rs   # Polars data extraction helpers
    │   │   ├── vector.rs      # Offline Candle vector search and cosine math
    │   │   ├── digest.rs      # RAG context formatting XML templates
    │   │   └── autopilot.rs   # Density-based query partition plan
    │   └── tests/             # Offline integration tests (wiremock)
    │
    ├── dnz-cli/               # CLI console wrapper application
    │   └── src/
    │       ├── lib.rs
    │       └── main.rs        # CLI argument router
    │
    ├── dnz-mcp/               # Model Context Protocol stdio server
    │   └── src/
    │       └── main.rs        # JSON-RPC protocol loop
    │
    └── dnz-python/            # Python FFI bindings via PyO3 & maturin
        └── src/
            └── lib.rs         # PyO3 modules exports
</code></pre>

    <h2>Internal Module Architecture</h2>
    <p>Core structures and serialization outputs flow directly into interface wrappers: </p>
    
    <div class="diagram-placeholder">
      <p><strong>DigitalNZ API</strong> &harr; <em>reqwest</em> &harr; <strong>dnz-core</strong> &rarr; <strong>JSON Models</strong> | <strong>Polars DataFrames</strong> | <strong>Vector Embeddings</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .diagram-placeholder {
    background-color: #0f172a;
    border: 1px dashed var(--border-color);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #38bdf8;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
</style>
